                                "type": "text",
                                "text": "I think sandstorm is totally worthy of its own thread. If I were to relate it back to SUA’s, I would say that the big distinctions I would make is that sandstorm is a single open source project where SUA’s aim to be more of an interoperable standard. Also sandstorm is"
